888
01:45:54,815 --> 01:45:57,807
Shackleford,
could you explain it to her?

889
01:45:57,951 --> 01:45:59,418
What?

890
01:46:00,787 --> 01:46:03,585
I could do that, sir.

891
01:46:03,724 --> 01:46:07,285
But I feel Ms Murphy
would rather hear it from you.

892
01:46:07,427 --> 01:46:10,191
OK. All right.

893
01:46:10,330 --> 01:46:14,096
She's the best of
the million-dollar club. Obviously.

894
01:46:17,537 --> 01:46:20,995
- "Million-dollar club"?
- Now you've got it.

895
01:46:22,909 --> 01:46:24,501
You told me you'd
never done that before.

896
01:46:24,644 --> 01:46:27,204
How many members
would you say there are?

897
01:46:28,081 --> 01:46:30,140
- Members?
- Yeah.

898
01:46:31,651 --> 01:46:34,245
- Worldwide?
- Yeah.

899
01:46:36,089 --> 01:46:37,647
I think a couple of dozen.

900
01:46:39,159 --> 01:46:41,753
Remember the one
that wouldn't stop hiccuping?

901
01:46:41,895 --> 01:46:44,887
- What?
- The waitress from Oklahoma.

902
01:46:45,031 --> 01:46:48,523
Every time you came near her,
she would convulse in hiccups.

903
01:46:50,604 --> 01:46:54,563
Yeah. I had forgotten. Quite a night.

904
01:46:56,643 --> 01:47:02,138
The best thing of it is that
you know if you're sexually compatible

