01:47:02,282 --> 01:47:04,546
right from the start.

906
01:47:15,095 --> 01:47:17,655
Shackleford, would you stop the car?

907
01:47:47,260 --> 01:47:49,228
Thank you, John.

908
01:47:53,266 --> 01:47:54,528
